_sText:
Decided to port my biggest map. I think I know how to port properly now. Tell me if there's any issues. I think there's some with lighting in two sections but it's pretty minor, and I wasn't sure how to fix it. 

Someone said that you're only a cool mapper once you name a map after yourself, so I did.

4 stage map, a fair lack of checkpoints for added "difficulty", block spam speedrun-style, nothing hard. Average time would be like 5-10 minutes or so?
